# ── Project-root .htaccess (§10.14) ──
# Belt-and-braces ONLY. The real control is that this directory is NOT under
# DocumentRoot — the addon domain points at public/, so nothing here is
# web-reachable in the first place. Apache 2.4 syntax (Require), not the
# deprecated 2.2 "Deny from all", and NOT <Directory> (invalid in .htaccess → 500).
Require all denied
